    {
      "text": "Popeye: Ijiwaru Majo Seahag no Maki (ポパイいじわる魔女シーハッグの巻, Popai Ijiwaru Majo Shīhaggu no Maki; lit. Popeye: The Tale of Sea Hag the Wicked Witch) is a video game for the Super Famicom game console based on the popular Popeye franchise. It was released by Technos Japan on August 12, 1994 exclusively in Japan.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "『ポパイ いじわる魔女シーハッグの巻』は、テクノスジャパンから1994年8月12日に発売された、スーパーファミコン用ビデオゲームソフト。すごろく＋横スクロールアクションゲーム。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "wikipedia_ja"
    },
    {
      "text": "Popeye: Ijiwaru Majo Seahag no Maki (ポパイいじわる魔女シーハッグの巻?) è un videogioco d'azione basato sul famoso personaggio di Braccio di Ferro, uscito per Super Famicom nel 1994.",
